Sadly, this was not the case:
- Five test participants could not complete the task in 30 minutes.
- One confused the difference between Groups versus Projects but could (inaccurately) recreate the structure in GitLab in approximately 3 minutes.
- Only one person was able to complete the task accurately in around 3 minutes.

