### Next steps
Currently, we are looking at how we can improve sharing groups and features. We want to [remove the barrier between groups and projects](https://gitlab.com/groups/gitlab-org/-/epics/2885). We believe that this will help with some of the problems users have with sharing across groups, and they will be able to take advantage of features that provide them with a more connected set of groups. This change will also improve our information architecture by reducing the confusion around how objects are connected, making navigation and cross-team sharing easier in the future.
